<h4 id="1å‡åŒ€åˆ†å¸ƒ"><strong>1ã€å‡åŒ€åˆ†å¸ƒ</strong></h4>
<p>å¯ä»¥ç›´æ¥ç”¨uniform()ç”Ÿæˆè‹¥å¹²æ•°ï¼Œå³ç¬¦åˆå‡åŒ€åˆ†å¸ƒï¼š</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">random_result</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
